{"tid":1237065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612唔係暴動但有人犯暴動罪？","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:08:25.000Z","uid":262035,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7a6f5c408e4f23d20feeb85cbd0bcdfa7a65b3","tid":1237065,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"大家不妨睇睇公安修例點定義<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴動</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴動<br />\n(1)如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動</strong></span>。  (由1970年第31號第12條修訂)<br />\n(2)任何人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">參與暴動，即犯暴動罪</span></strong></span> &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁10年；及<br />\n(b)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁5年。<br />\n<br />\n請問盧處長點樣可以無暴動但有人犯暴動罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1832ac49125840c4f9cc0d37172f59122f0f6084","tid":1237065,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"一人唔叫暴動，叫襲警，佢都唔撚知自己講乜"},{"pid":"76d293615cfdd027cec2eb245d92dc0b371f6340","tid":1237065,"uid":79085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"唔係暴動 但係告人暴動罪<br />\n唔係濫暴 但係開槍打9你<br />\n唔係卸膊 但係話係當場指揮官決定<br />\n唔係狗 但係冇人性"}]}